glish (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/msPutPropertyEnabled\"><code>msPutPropertyEnabled()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><em><code>removeProperty()</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/setProperty\"><code>setProperty()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for CSSOM</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent\"><code>AnimationEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSS\"><code>CSS</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSConditionRule\"><code>CSSConditionRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSGroupingRule\"><code>CSSGroupingRule</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSKeyframeRule\"><code>CSSKeyframeRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSKeyframesRule\"><code>CSSKeyframesRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSMediaRule\"><code>CSSMediaRule</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSNamespaceRule\"><code>CSSNamespaceRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSPageRule\"><code>CSSPageRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSRule\"><code>CSSRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSRuleList\"><code>CSSRuleList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleRule\"><code>CSSStyleRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleSheet\"><code>CSSStyleSheet</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSSupportsRule\"><code>CSSSupportsRule</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CaretPosition\"><code>CaretPosition</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList\"><code>MediaQueryList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Screen\"><code>Screen</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet\"><code>StyleSheet</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/StyleSheetList\"><code>StyleSheetList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TransitionEvent\"><code>TransitionEvent</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><code>CSSStyleDeclaration.removeProperty()</code>&nbsp;方法移除 style 对象的一个属性。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> oldValue <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> style<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">removeProperty</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>property<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参数","title":"参数","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><em><code>property</code></em>&nbsp;是一个&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a> ，代表要移除的属性名。注意由多个单词组成的属性要用连字符连接各个单词，不接收驼峰命名法的形式。</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"返回值","title":"返回值","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><code><em>oldValue</em></code> 是一个 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a> ，等于被移除的属性在移除前的属性值。</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"异常","title":"异常","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMException\"><code>DOMException</code></a>&nbsp;NO_MODIFICATION_ALLOWED_ERR: 如果属性或声明块为只读，抛出此异常。</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例子","title":"例子","isH3":false,"content":"<p>下面的 JavaScript 代码从样式表里移除了&nbsp;<code>margin</code>&nbsp;属性：</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> declaration <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>styleSheets<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>rules<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>style<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> oldValue <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> declaration<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">removeProperty</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'margin'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"Specifications","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/cssom/#dom-cssstyledeclaration-removeproperty\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Object Model (CSSOM)<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">CSSStyleDeclaration.removeProperty()</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">Working Draft</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-Style/css.html#CSS-CSSStyleDeclaration\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Document Object Model (DOM) Level 2 Style Specification<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">CSSStyleDeclaration</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-obsolete\">Obsolete</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器支持情况","id":"浏览器支持情况","isH3":false,"query":"api.CSSStyleDeclaration.removeProperty","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/removeProperty/bcd.json"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"例子","id":"例子"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"浏览器支持情况","id":"浏览器支持情况"}],"summary":"CSSStyleDeclaration.removeProperty() 方法移除 style 对象的一个属性。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"CSSStyleDeclaration.removeProperty()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"CSSStyleDeclaration.removeProperty()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/cssstyledeclaration/removeproperty","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/cssstyledeclaration/removeproperty/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration","title":"CSSStyleDeclaration"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/removeProperty","title":"CSSStyleDeclaration.removeProperty()"}],"pageTitle":"CSSStyleDeclaration.removeProperty() - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}